Title: Filet Frenzy
Description:
The sockeye salmon are running, there are great numbers rushing up the rivers of the Azure Span.

Have you ever tasted fresh salmon? <Marl holds his hand to his lips and gives the classic chef's kiss>

Please explorer gather or fish up 12 Sockeye Salmon and we will have a great menu of salmon for the week.

Oh, I should mention that the bears of the span 'really' like salmon as well, so be careful, but they might just help you with the fishing. <The chef winks at you.>
